## Tuning tips

| Goal | Change |
|------|--------|
| Train faster (no window) | `RENDER = False` in train.py (default) |
| Watch training live | `RENDER = True` in train.py |
| Harder ball | Increase `BALL_SPEED` in pong_env.py |
| Smaller paddle | Decrease `PADDLE_H` in pong_env.py |
| More exploration | Increase `epsilon_decay` closer to 1.0 |
| Longer training | Increase `EPISODES` in train.py |